entries.femaleVariant: Get your head out of the clouds. We won't get across. No way.
You see that goddamn Great Wall? Not a crack. Not even a rat's dick could squeeze through.
Look, people built that wall. And to err is human.
Borders slip and slide. You can't slice up the earth, just like you can't divide the heavens.
Looks like a pretty solid slab of concrete to me.
Be patient. You'll see soon enough.
We'll be on the other side before you know it.
